text: Embark on a journey of opulence in this meticulously crafted residence. Thoughtfully designed floor plan, elegance & comfort abound around every corner; including the vaulted ceiling with beam accents in living rm, primary w/fireplace, luxe ensuite & unparalleled his/her closets. Indulge in the gourmet kitchen featuring quartz, high-end Thermador appliances & walk-in pantry, while in the laundry rm adds practicality & function w/tile dog wash. The 4+car garage w/shop & lower lvl patio offer ample space & room to expand outdoor living. Abundant storage ensures effortless organization. Nestled in a private gated community, relish panoramic vistas of Cascades, Cornet Bay & beyond. Experience luxury living at its finest in this remarkable home.

Imagine owning a luxurious custom-built home that offers breathtaking views of the Bellingham Channel and Ship Harbor, serving as your gateway to the enchanting San Juan Islands. This three-level masterpiece is designed with your comfort in mind, featuring an elevator for easy access. On the main floor, you'll discover a versatile studio with a convenient kitchenette and a separate entrance, perfect for guests or a home office. As you ascend to the upper level, the primary suite awaits, boasting panoramic views, vaulted ceiling, a spacious walk-in closet, double vanities & a luxurious walk-in shower. High end features include, granite & quartz countertops, Thermador appliances & Timbertek composite decking to name a few. A stunning home!

Discover a breathtaking multi-level home commanding stunning views of Rainbow Bridge, Shelter Bay Marina, and the picturesque golf course. This distinctive property boasts unique features such as grand beams and wood columns, inviting you into a world of architectural marvels. Immerse yourself in natural light streaming through two-story picture windows, illuminating the spacious interior with warmth and charm. Ascend the floating staircase to find a loft primary bedroom, offering unparalleled vistas and a sense of serenity. Welcome to your sanctuary overlooking beauty at every turn. Leased land. Shelter bay offers a marina, golf course, beach access, pool and golf course. Come make this home yours!

Low maintenance rambler in a great neighborhood. Great home for downsizing, first home or long-term investment. In great shape and move in ready. Great street appeal and backs up to a quiet greenbelt area. Freshly painted exterior and new roof to be installed Mid-April.

Immerse yourself in the enchanting embrace of country charm with this captivating 1.5-story farm-style residence! Featuring 3 bedrooms, 1.5 baths nestled on 9.8 acres of prime farmland. Every corner of this property exudes warmth and tranquility. Step into the expansive living room with a large window inviting the beauty of the rural landscape into your home with each glance. Indulge your equestrian passions with the barn's 5 horse stalls and a shop. Lush fruit trees and garden plots await your green thumb, promising an oasis of natural abundance. Conveniently located near town amenities, this property offers the perfect balance of rural serenity and urban convenience. Don't miss this exceptional opportunity. Call or book a tour today!

Welcome to your new home in Concrete! This charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom residence boasts 1680 sq ft of spacious living, complete with a dedicated flex space for an office or additional bedroom, you decide. Nestled in a prime location, outdoor enthusiasts will delight in the abundance of nearby activities, from scenic hikes to tranquil fishing spots along the Skagit River. Affordability meets comfort with this property, offering a fenced-in yard perfect for your furry companions to roam freely. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this inviting haven yours!

Manufactured home in well kept 55+ park 2bed 2 bath home features new flooring, remodeled master bathroom with soaking tub. Conveniently located to all your needs: shopping, dining, Riverside Health Club, and Coffee Barn to name a few of your potential new favorites. Buyer must to be approved to park.

Amazing fully remodeled gem in town and close to everything! This one checks all the boxes: tons of natural light streaming through the all new windows, brand new appliances, new mini-split heat and A/C, new carpet, tile, and LVP flooring, covered front porch and back deck. Fresh paint both in and out, clean and dry basement cellar, detached garage with 220v and new garage door, garden space, RV parking, and more. Don't miss this fantastic opportunity!

Enjoy Country living with this custom 4br 1.75ba partially upgraded home on 4.97 ac that is fenced for horses with round pen and a 3 stall barn with power and water. This 1 1/2 story 1960 sq ft home features a lg living rm with cozy woodstove and slider to patio. Primary bedroom is on ground floor with slider to patio and attached 3/4ba, huge family rm and dining rm with LVP flooring and French doors to backyard, open kitchen w/SS appliances, upstairs there is 3 bedrooms and a full bath and a lg 2 car attached garage, propane heating and private well. Also there is a 36x28 huge shop/barn with carport for plenty of storage and loads of extra parking. This property may qualify for Seller Financing (Vendee). Sold as is.

Cozy, turn of the century home, right in the heart of downtown Burlington. Just a short distance to shopping, restaurants, park and library! Home offers just over 1100sq ft with 3 bedrooms, 1.75 baths. Beautiful renovated kitchen and hall bathroom! original hardwood, newer windows. Fruit trees in backyard and flat area for garden. Super cute shed in backyard with electricity and built in cabinets. RV space with clean out station. This home is completely fenced in backyard!

Westside location across bridge from Mount Vernon featuring a classic tri level home on 1/2 acre in a peaceful county setting. Beautiful view of Mount Baker and across the valley from your own living room. 2224 sq ft, Formal LR, DR, Kitchen w/ eating nook, 3 bedrooms and full bath up, spacious family room downstairs with large laundry room. Hobby room off the garage. 28 x48 pole building with enclosed shop area and 12x 12 equipment storage. PUD water, updated septic system in 2016, triple paine windows, 2 fireplaces that run on propane, cedar siding, Heat pump, flood insurance approx. $500.00 per year.

Discover an unparalleled opportunity to own a fee-simple medium bank waterfront retreat boasting breathtaking, uninterrupted views that mesmerize, especially during captivating sunsets. Immerse yourself in the tranquil ambiance of shore living, with the soothing rhythm of waves as your backdrop. Indulge in private beach access on both sides of the residence. Revel in the amenities including tennis court, a boat ramp, clubhouse, and BBQ facilities. This updated two-bedroom, 1.75-bathroom home presents functional yet elegant spaces adorned with beautiful finishes.

Nestled within the Pressentin Creek neighborhood, this charming home offers a serene .58-acre level lot. Large 1782 square-foot manufactured home has 3 beds, 2 baths with a office/den. Open living room into dinning and kitchen. This home sits on a full concrete slab foundation with concrete blocking. Metal roof makes it perfectly low maintenance. Ample room for RVs, boats, and more, right on your property along with a wood shed and kennel for a dog. No flood insurance needed here!

First time on the market! This stunning rambler style duplex is well maintained and ready for new owners. Great investment for owner occupied buyer, investor or multigenerational living. Total sqr ft is 2876. Side A: 3 bdrms & 1.75 baths in 1516 sqr ft. Open floor plan, lrg kitchen w/oak cabinets, eating bar & dining area. 2 car tandem garage with W/D. Side B: 2 large bdrms plus an office, 1.75 baths in 1360 Sqr ft. Unit B upgrades: AC, laminate vinyl plank flooring, granite ctps, newer applcs. Open floor concept w/ dining area, eating bar and gas fireplace. Oversized 1 car garage. Large carport cover, RV parking w/ hook ups, circular drive, covered back deck & shop/shed. Convenient location to the YMCA, shopping, medical and all amenities.

Light & Bright Skagit Highlands home, ready for new owners! Spacious open-concept main floor plan boasting tall ceilings, laminate flooring, a spacious living room, open dining area, and the kitchen with a breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances. Upstairs is a versatile family/flex area, perfect for a home gym or office! Shared full bath, conveniently-located laundry, and 4 bedrooms including the expansive primary suite with walk-in closet and 5-piece ensuite with lovely mountain views. Fully-fenced backyard with a covered patio, open patio, and plenty of room for hobbies and entertaining. Attached garage, community park/playground, located near shops, restaurants, parks, the Skagit River, and commuter routes. Welcome Home!

Excellent craftsman style home in the sought after Gateway Heights neighborhood of Sedro Woolley. Backing up to highly desirable green space allowing you to create your own little oasis. This home is conveniently located near hiking trails & parks. Cozy living room greets you w/ warm fireplace for those chilly PNW days, leading into the tactfully located kitchen w/ granite counters & stainless appliances overlooking the deck & large yard. Follow the stairs to the upper level where three bedrooms are located. The primary offers ample space, walk in closet & an en-suite bathroom complete w/ double vanity & window, allowing natural light in during the day. W/D are conveniently located on the second level as well. Don't miss this great home!

Welcome to this charming home nestled on the edge of Burlington in a picturesque neighborhood. Enjoy an updated kitchen with granite countertops, newer stainless steel appliances, a roomy pantry, breakfast bar, and separate dining area. Relax in the spacious living room with a cozy fireplace and retreat to one of the three generous bedrooms, including a primary suite with a sizable walk-in closet. Situated as an end unit on a tranquil dead-end street with a private park, this residence is an ideal place to call home.

Dream retreat nestled in a charming community, boasting Nantucket-style allure w/beautiful water & island views! This two-level haven offers convenience with the primary bedroom on the main floor, complete with a private balcony for serene moments. Delight in culinary adventures in the expansive kitchen, featuring granite countertops & an inviting island with seating. Cozy up by the fireplace in the living room & relish outdoor gatherings on the covered porch, soaking in the captivating scenery. Plus, enjoy recreational amenities including a pickleball sports court and trail directly to the beach ensuring endless entertainment for you and your loved ones. Live the coastal lifestyle you've always envisioned in this exquisite abode.

This great property is like having two homes in one! Looking for multi-generational living? Investment property? Live in one side and rent the other? With a total of 4 bedrooms, 2.75 bathrooms, two kitchens, two living spaces, two laundry rooms, & even two separate entrances, this property has endless possibilities for the next owner. Situated on a corner lot giving a large, fully fenced in yard with gated entries, an attached storage shed on the back patio and ample parking. Within walking distance to downtown Sedro-Woolley, parks and schools and ten minutes to the freeway.

This charming 2 bed, 2 bath rambler boasts a spacious living & dining area filled with natural light. Enjoy your cozy gas fireplace. Beautiful engineered hardwood flooring throughout. Full bath off Primary bedroom. Great size kitchen w/lots of storage and gas range/oven. Adorned w/granite counters, slate floors/backsplash, and SS appliances. Fresh interior & exterior paint. Fully fenced backyard with large covered patio and raised beds for gardening. Enjoy your hot tub and the peace and quiet of this great neighborhood. Bonus room in garage, currently used as a workshop/storage; possible office, 3rd bedroom? Home located close to the medical district, schools, Kiwanis park, shopping, and I-5. Your very own RV parking and guess what? NO HOA!

Pride in ownership is an understatement for this meticulous mountain retreat. Tucked into the North Cascades Mountains, or the American Alps, this picturesque single-level house & 762 sq ft ADU has everything for idyllic country living. Custom built 3-bd, 2-bth main house w/newer bamboo flooring, plus a fully permitted ADU, w/bonus finished space above for a bdrm or office. Both structures have brand new roofs, cedar siding & are wired for generators. New 25kW Grid-tied solar array, designed to fully offset electrical needs + new heat pump/AC. Private Skagit River beach access through HOA. Spacious yard, beautiful landscaping & established garden. Opportunities for this quality of homestead on 5+ acres are rare. Don't miss your chance!

Discover serene living with this single-level, light-filled, 3-bed rambler in the heart of Gibralter. Allow nature to delight you while enjoying panoramic bay, mountain, and Deception Pass State Park views from the expansive back deck. The spacious interior and flowing floor plan features endless vistas from one end to the other. Cook gourmet meals in the open kitchen with island and eating nook overlooking the bay. Large primary suite with walk-in closet and 5-piece en suite bath with jetted tub. Encapsulated by a manicured lawn and garden beds, the outdoor enjoyment is endless. Large 3-car garage. The cherry on top: private beach access, moorage, and tideland rights provide a lifestyle enriched with natural beauty and bayside allure.

Welcome to 2510 Briarwood Circle where the charm of this 3 bed 2 bath rambler is immediately apparent upon arrival. The covered front porch invites you into a space where light and warmth abound. Cooks will love the cozy yet functional eat in kitchen, equipped with stainless-steel appliances and a gas range. The southern exposure of this property bathes the interior in natural light creating a light and bright living space. A 2 car garage and spacious driveway offer ample parking and storage solutions. Entertainment and relaxation opportunities are endless with a fully fenced backyard, large side deck for gatherings, and a garden shed to house all your outdoor tools. Perfect location with easy access to parks, schools and the YMCA.

INVESTOR ALERT! This under construction home is situated on 1.73 acres with over 100 ft. of riverfront. This home is a canvas for your finishing and personal touches with major upgrades done: all new siding, windows, re-leveled, re-structured roof w/new cross beams, Zip System sheathing (R-9), electrical panel (200 amps), and much, much more. Outdoor amenities include partially fenced pasture, barn w/electrical, chicken coop, RV/boat parking, and a riverfront fishing shack. All above the floodplain! This great investment opportunity awaits, schedule a showing today! Previous Buyer got Cold Feet

This brand new collection of NW contemporary cottage homes built by Strandberg Construction, located at The Crossings, is the perfect balance of spaces designed both for privacy and community. Poised against the lily pad covered pond w/walking trails, a community garden & gathering spaces throughout. Styled with modern touches, this cottage has a main level owner's suite w/elegant bath & an inviting farmhouse kitchen ready for your grand celebrations. 2 additional bedrooms and full bath up. Clear cedar detailing, solar panels, single car+ garage and drought resistant landscaping. Built net-zero these cottages enjoy a healthy respect for the incredible natural surroundings & will offer extremely low utility expenses & a 5k+ tax credit.

This enchanting 1900's farm house will capture your heart. From the moment you arrive, you will feel a sense of serenity and connection with nature. Set on a sunny, level .87-acre lot, gardeners will enjoy reaping what they sow from their private orchard, veggie and flower gardens. This spacious 4 bed + den home is flooded with natural light. It has been mindfully updated over the years, yet retains period charm. Main level primary bed with en-suite 3/4 bath and walk-in-closet. Large, open kitchen with eat-up bar and gas range. Home office is in a quiet corner of the main level. Store ALL of your toys and tools in the 1400+ sft detached garage with HUGE shop. Darling hobby/potting shed. Host Tulip Festival parties on the entertainment deck.
